com.ihealth.communication.control

Class Bg5Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ihealth.communication.control.Bg5Profile

  • public class Bg5Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    Public APIs for the Bg5 serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager#registerClient register. When new data from Bg5 device, The CallbackiHealthDevicesCallback#onDeviceNotify can be triggered should call.
